; Coverage for balance.cc lot sorting in balance

2024/01/01 Buy Lot 1
    Assets:Stock     5 AAPL {$100} [2024/01/01]
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Buy Lot 2
    Assets:Stock     3 AAPL {$120} [2024/02/01]
    Assets:Cash

test bal Assets:Stock --lots --lot-dates
5 AAPL {$100} [2024/01/01]
3 AAPL {$120} [2024/02/01]  Assets:Stock
end test
